{"tid":2402259,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商人涉毆打反國安法街站人士受審 辯稱觸碰純屬意外","createTime":"2021-02-10T10:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T10:49:04.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7f39a32f0728108f04783515e2f458f603a86c","tid":2402259,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:25:22.000Z","msg":"深水埗區議員劉家衡去年5月擺街站反對港區國安法，其間一名持不同政見男子疑到場<span class=\"red\">用煙蒂燙傷劉的男秘書</span>，又涉<span class=\"red\">出手抓傷區議員李文浩的女秘書</span>。滋事男原本被控在公眾地方打鬥罪，及後遭改控普通襲擊罪，案件今於西九龍法院開審。女秘書供稱，當時見被告不斷拉扯男秘書的衣領，遂上前分隔二人，其間遭被告打頭及抓傷。辯方聲稱，實情是街站職員先對被告出言不遜，又以膠板打他頭部，被告才會拉扯男秘書。<br />\n<br />\n被告眼鏡批發商人<span class=\"red\">尹載道</span>（49 歲）被控一項普通襲擊罪"},{"pid":"89ef57cb841233553d25fb6e1313aeb591e541bc","tid":2402259,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/GNNXK7AOFVHFPEFG2U5ZXVWVBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FGNNXK7AOFVHFPEFG2U5ZXVWVBA%2F&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGheEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=ddd97f9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FGNNXK7AOFVHFPEFG2U5ZXVWVBA%2F&h=7cd3e033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/GNNXK7AOFVHFPEFG2U5ZXVWVBA/</a>"},{"pid":"36bdf0e0bd3659e76cbd7cc8164fee91e1d2a3b4","tid":2402259,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"有片斷正"},{"pid":"ff13df3d6263658adde5feeb4e40cbbffa779052","tid":2402259,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T10:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9951fd1d3fc6559b0ac6a1a973ef481279a13bfd","tid":2402259,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score